body.section: Hierarchy PreviousCesareanDelivery is a kind of RiskFactor

section.title: Description
section.p: [US Standard Certificate Of Birth Field 41]. If the RiskFactor encountered during this pregnancy is "Mother had a previous cesarean delivery" this subclass of RiskFactor is used to contain the number of previous cesarean deliveries.

stentry.p: [US Standard Certificate Of Birth Field 41]. The number of previous cesarean deliveries experienced by the infant's mother prior to this pregnancy.
